WEBVTT

01:35.740 --> 01:41.280
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.280 --> 01:43.930
[Episode 40]

01:47.509 --> 01:49.840
Since His Majesty lacks virtue,

01:53.560 --> 01:55.590
we might as well have him abdicate.

02:06.430 --> 02:07.430
Yigui.

02:08.410 --> 02:09.940
Be careful with your words.

02:13.800 --> 02:15.430
What you said today—

02:16.070 --> 02:16.800
neither I

02:17.700 --> 02:19.430
nor my ministers here

02:20.770 --> 02:22.530
heard a word of it.

02:26.470 --> 02:27.870
Let's continue drinking

02:28.280 --> 02:29.150
and enjoy

02:30.400 --> 02:31.930
this wonderful moment together.

02:31.930 --> 02:36.670
[Bearing Virtue, Bestowing Kindness]

02:33.190 --> 02:34.630
Only the few of us knew about

02:34.630 --> 02:36.880
that remark about abdication back then.

02:36.880 --> 02:40.840
[Hear All Sides]

02:37.750 --> 02:38.750
Could it be that

02:39.310 --> 02:40.750
someone snitched?

02:49.260 --> 02:51.190
It wasn't that I was being foolish.

02:51.470 --> 02:54.400
The Late Emperor was autocratic
and muddle-headed,

02:54.510 --> 02:56.710
making life unbearable for the people.

02:57.310 --> 02:59.160
And he feared that

02:59.360 --> 03:01.000
the Crown Prince's virtue
had spread far and wide,

03:01.000 --> 03:02.400
so he deliberately propped up

03:02.400 --> 03:04.660
the Jia family and the Sixteenth Prince.

03:07.030 --> 03:08.280
If, back then,

03:08.500 --> 03:11.630
with the combined power of
the Xie, Wei, and Qi families,

03:12.020 --> 03:15.180
we had put Crown Prince Chengde
on the throne,

03:16.190 --> 03:19.190
would the realm have been
well-governed and at peace?

03:21.710 --> 03:23.630
Crown Prince Chengde

03:24.280 --> 03:26.000
was too indecisive

03:26.590 --> 03:28.560
and lost the initiative.

03:31.680 --> 03:34.800
The Crown Prince and Linshan
died in battle.

03:35.430 --> 03:36.630
And you, Grand Tutor,

03:37.000 --> 03:39.000
have been depressed and sidelined.

03:39.120 --> 03:39.870
Tell me—

03:40.120 --> 03:42.150
would I have turned myself in?

03:44.079 --> 03:46.210
Crown Prince Chengde did say back then

03:46.430 --> 03:49.280
that although Li Xing came from
a clean background,

03:49.280 --> 03:51.030
he was obsessed with power.

03:51.030 --> 03:51.800
Could it be...

03:51.800 --> 03:52.690
Therefore,

03:52.910 --> 03:54.750
when the Crown Prince decided
to go to Jinzhou,

03:54.750 --> 03:57.400
it was already a lost cause.

03:58.030 --> 04:00.030
The Crown Prince was muddle-headed

04:00.840 --> 04:03.500
and allowed himself to be swayed
by sycophants,

04:03.750 --> 04:07.560
even daring to plot to replace me.

04:09.080 --> 04:12.170
What do you make of it, Sui?

04:12.280 --> 04:14.470
Your Majesty is wise and will make
the proper decision.

04:12.350 --> 04:17.410
[Lord Changxin, Sui Tuo]

04:14.710 --> 04:16.360
I've long been stationed in the Northwest

04:16.360 --> 04:18.560
and know little of the court's affairs,

04:18.720 --> 04:20.720
so I dare not speak presumptuously.

04:27.870 --> 04:30.160
For the sake of the realm,

04:31.720 --> 04:32.720
I

04:33.600 --> 04:36.200
have no choice but do the unthinkable.

04:36.560 --> 04:40.159
Nephew, will you aid me?

04:41.000 --> 04:45.110
You are my sister's son.

04:46.430 --> 04:50.390
You've got our Qi family's blood
running through your veins.

04:52.060 --> 04:53.710
Your Majesty means...

05:01.070 --> 05:06.160
I wish to share the realm with you

05:07.430 --> 05:09.960
and form an everlasting alliance.

05:17.630 --> 05:22.510
The Late Emperor gave Lord Changxin
an empty promise

05:22.780 --> 05:25.430
and had him hold back his troops.

05:26.710 --> 05:28.110
To eliminate his own son,

05:28.480 --> 05:30.810
he even invited the fox
into the hen house.

05:31.600 --> 05:33.800
He was truly a man without virtue.

05:35.390 --> 05:36.430
The Late Emperor

05:36.780 --> 05:44.250
[Qingyuan Palace]

05:37.070 --> 05:40.330
forged a letter in Rongyin's handwriting
and sent it to me,

05:40.510 --> 05:43.970
forcing me to turn back to the Capital
from the rescue mission.

05:46.510 --> 05:47.360
Yan.

05:47.480 --> 05:49.430
While the fire's still raging, run now.

05:49.430 --> 05:50.070
No.

05:50.420 --> 05:51.570
We leave together!

05:53.950 --> 05:55.120
Lord Wei, you...

05:55.140 --> 05:56.850
If I hadn't made a sacrifice
to save myself,

05:55.909 --> 05:59.900
[Qingyuan Palace]

05:57.510 --> 06:00.510
I'd have been labeled a traitor
who defiled the harem,

06:00.600 --> 06:01.860
and the entire Wei clan

06:02.160 --> 06:04.650
would have been exterminated.

06:04.720 --> 06:08.220
[Qingyuan Palace]

06:05.000 --> 06:05.750
Go away!

06:06.950 --> 06:07.920
Yan.

06:08.930 --> 06:09.810
You go first.

06:14.630 --> 06:15.510
Rongyin!

06:17.630 --> 06:20.140
Don't worry. Leave this to me.

06:29.720 --> 06:34.360
For 3 generations, the Xie, Qi, and Wei families
have served Great Yin with absolute loytalty,

06:34.360 --> 06:37.210
fighting bloody battles
until our kin were all but wiped out.

06:37.210 --> 06:39.409
What right did that cursed emperor have

06:39.680 --> 06:41.830
to toy with us like that?

06:48.850 --> 06:50.640
As for what happened next,

06:51.480 --> 06:53.680
I assume you already know, Grand Tutor.

06:54.920 --> 06:57.890
I was the one
who bathed the imperial palace in blood.

06:58.120 --> 06:59.650
If I hadn't staged the coup,

07:00.190 --> 07:02.120
what other choice would I have had?

07:07.680 --> 07:09.720
After Rongyin passed away,

07:10.600 --> 07:12.920
I had no choice but to seize
that cursed emperor by the throat

07:12.920 --> 07:15.450
and force him to write
an edict of abdication.

07:18.040 --> 07:19.920
Only with me in charge of the court

07:21.000 --> 07:23.270
could Great Yin remain stable

07:25.270 --> 07:28.680
and the state be preserved.

07:34.630 --> 07:36.190
As for Wei Qilin's infamy,

07:36.190 --> 07:38.510
I had no choice but to force it upon him.

07:38.510 --> 07:41.159
It was only because the Late Emperor

07:41.159 --> 07:43.300
had schemed far too meticulously.

07:43.950 --> 07:45.950
Before returning to the Capital,
I handed the Tiger Tally

07:45.950 --> 07:48.630
to my most trusted subordinate, Wei Qilin,

07:48.750 --> 07:50.680
and had him request reinforcements
on my behalf.

07:50.680 --> 07:51.540
Your Highness.

07:51.870 --> 07:53.320
This Tiger Tally is real.

07:53.390 --> 07:55.250
Please send troops immediately!

07:55.480 --> 07:57.120
This Tiger Tally is fake.

07:57.390 --> 07:58.600
It doesn't match.

07:59.630 --> 08:03.360
Everything was within
the Late Emperor's calculations all along.

08:07.640 --> 08:09.710
Later, misled by Qi Min,

08:10.040 --> 08:13.170
Zheng reinvestigated the Jinzhou case
from 17 years ago

08:13.510 --> 08:16.510
and unexpectedly discovered that
Wei Qilin's family was still alive.

08:16.510 --> 08:17.770
Only by silencing them

08:18.390 --> 08:21.040
could I preserve our bond
as uncle and nephew.

08:21.160 --> 08:22.070
Who would have thought—

08:22.070 --> 08:23.870
human plans are no match for
heaven's will.

08:23.870 --> 08:26.270
Zheng ended up being saved by Changyu.

08:27.680 --> 08:29.560
It seems fate had other plans.

08:37.140 --> 08:38.490
This truly is a case of

08:41.240 --> 08:46.630
an emperor abusing his power
while his loyal subjects die unjustly.

08:50.070 --> 08:51.260
So,

08:53.040 --> 08:55.800
I lost in the end.

09:07.810 --> 09:08.780
Shall we go in?

09:21.400 --> 09:22.230
Let's go.

09:28.910 --> 09:30.080
Fortunately,

09:30.270 --> 09:31.750
the blade that is Xie Zheng

09:31.750 --> 09:33.630
has found its scabbard—

09:34.550 --> 09:35.600
Fan Changyu.

09:37.320 --> 09:39.720
Let me borrow a line from Changyu:

09:40.480 --> 09:42.870
"be a good pig in this life,

09:43.630 --> 09:44.840
and a good person

09:45.910 --> 09:48.080
in the next."

09:55.120 --> 09:57.030
People like me

09:59.460 --> 10:01.870
will probably fall straight into hell.

10:06.360 --> 10:08.760
I'm afraid there won't be
a next life for me.

10:19.200 --> 10:21.240
Little wooden horse,

10:22.120 --> 10:24.720
running clip-clop.

10:25.150 --> 10:31.630
Little boy, spirits high.

10:32.960 --> 10:38.480
Sword in hand, singing loud.

10:39.960 --> 10:46.240
I'll chase all of you away.

11:00.630 --> 11:02.430
It's time for the morning court.

11:02.720 --> 11:03.690
Morning court.

11:03.960 --> 11:04.870
Morning court.

11:08.150 --> 11:09.190
My dear ministers,

11:09.190 --> 11:11.050
what do you have to report to me?

11:11.790 --> 11:14.120
Prime Minister Wei, why are you kneeling?

11:14.810 --> 11:16.350
Am I that scary?

11:17.910 --> 11:19.240
Never mind. Never mind.

11:19.240 --> 11:21.630
If there's nothing else,
court is dismissed.

11:21.630 --> 11:23.780
It seems this empire

11:24.330 --> 11:26.050
can only rely on me after all.

11:27.140 --> 11:29.900
Rely on me. Rely on me.

11:31.220 --> 11:32.010
Brother.

11:35.030 --> 11:37.080
Look what treats I brought you.

11:39.280 --> 11:41.010
These are all your favorites.

11:41.040 --> 11:42.240
Candied plums,

11:43.600 --> 11:45.240
and your favorite osmanthus cakes.

11:45.240 --> 11:46.840
Come on, have a bite.

11:51.320 --> 11:53.150
Delicious. Delicious.

11:55.910 --> 11:58.100
Eat slowly. Don't choke.

12:00.960 --> 12:01.750
Delicious.

12:02.870 --> 12:03.720
Brother,

12:05.440 --> 12:06.840
do you still recognize

12:08.000 --> 12:09.200
who I am?

12:33.270 --> 12:34.600
W-What?

12:37.270 --> 12:38.000
Brother...

12:38.040 --> 12:39.320
What did you say?

12:40.830 --> 12:42.570
I am wise? That's right.

12:44.390 --> 12:45.440
What did you say?

13:08.960 --> 13:11.790
I thought you wouldn't come.

13:15.090 --> 13:16.890
I had to see you off one last time.

13:18.320 --> 13:19.650
You may break your word,

13:21.190 --> 13:22.040
but I won't.

13:23.190 --> 13:24.190
It was kind of you

13:25.630 --> 13:27.630
to make this soup especially for me.

13:28.910 --> 13:30.310
I appreciate the effort.

13:31.240 --> 13:33.170
Even ordinary death row prisoners

13:33.670 --> 13:35.270
get a last meal before heading to

13:35.270 --> 13:37.200
the execution ground, don't they?

13:38.670 --> 13:39.750
Feed me.

13:41.080 --> 13:43.010
Don't let your efforts go to waste.

14:15.480 --> 14:16.360
What's wrong?

14:17.720 --> 14:18.780
Can't bear to do it?

14:37.120 --> 14:38.520
It was brewed well.

14:40.190 --> 14:41.520
It's just a bit cold.

14:49.720 --> 14:50.790
Do you know

14:51.670 --> 14:53.030
when I

14:53.440 --> 14:54.570
truly fell for you?

14:56.760 --> 14:57.520
I do.

14:58.900 --> 15:00.760
But if I could do it all over again,

15:02.400 --> 15:04.800
I definitely wouldn't have pulled you out.

15:05.730 --> 15:07.210
You're the only one

15:07.720 --> 15:09.200
who didn't look afraid

15:09.960 --> 15:11.160
after seeing my face.

15:12.070 --> 15:13.400
This is a reward for you.

15:35.480 --> 15:36.970
I saw in you

15:37.690 --> 15:39.900
something I had longed for all along—

15:42.630 --> 15:43.510
freedom.

15:49.120 --> 15:50.630
You once had it too.

15:52.000 --> 15:53.530
It was right in front of you,

15:55.300 --> 15:57.360
but your mask kept you from seeing it.

16:04.440 --> 16:05.440
Thank you

16:06.440 --> 16:07.700
for keeping your word.

16:10.460 --> 16:11.920
You hate me so much,

16:14.080 --> 16:15.790
yet you still granted my wish.

16:19.320 --> 16:20.360
Yu Qianqian,

16:21.440 --> 16:23.470
I really like you a lot.

16:25.870 --> 16:26.990
Therefore,

16:28.200 --> 16:29.720
if there's a next life,

16:31.120 --> 16:32.060
I hope

16:33.780 --> 16:35.440
we never meet again.

16:39.700 --> 16:40.700
Is there any left?

16:41.830 --> 16:43.160
Don't let it go to waste.

17:14.160 --> 17:15.440
This is the end.

17:17.670 --> 17:19.579
You once told me

17:20.440 --> 17:21.400
that if you died,

17:21.680 --> 17:22.880
you could go back.

17:25.310 --> 17:26.750
I want to know

17:28.790 --> 17:30.330
who you are really—

17:34.320 --> 17:35.870
a wandering spirit,

17:37.530 --> 17:39.110
or a fallen immortal?

17:40.590 --> 17:42.010
Tell me.

17:44.240 --> 17:46.350
I want to die knowing the truth.

17:50.770 --> 17:51.920
I'm just me.

17:53.720 --> 17:54.960
I'm Yu Qianqian.

18:00.200 --> 18:00.960
You...

18:02.570 --> 18:04.570
You liar.

18:47.300 --> 18:48.420
Are you all right?

18:58.920 --> 18:59.830
Changyu.

19:00.350 --> 19:01.680
I have a secret.

19:04.110 --> 19:06.750
I came from a place far, far away.

19:07.810 --> 19:09.410
I might not be able to go back.

19:12.040 --> 19:13.200
If it's too far,

19:14.070 --> 19:15.360
then don't go back.

19:16.080 --> 19:17.250
Let's go back to Lin'an

19:17.250 --> 19:18.710
and live a good life there.

19:28.110 --> 19:28.890
Let's go.

19:51.190 --> 19:54.380
[Yin]

19:53.160 --> 19:54.790
[In the 18th year of Yongping,]

19:53.480 --> 19:57.300
♪ The world is vast ♪

19:55.160 --> 19:58.860
[the name Yu Bao'er was officially
entered into the Imperial Genealogy.]

19:58.860 --> 20:04.840
♪ The storm is rising ♪

19:59.480 --> 20:03.000
[His mother Empress Dowager Yu
renamed him Qi Yu.]

20:03.750 --> 20:08.830
[In mid-spring of that year, the new Emperor
ascended the throne and proclaimed the era Yongxing.]

20:06.510 --> 20:10.750
♪ Day and night ♪

20:09.750 --> 20:13.400
[He honored his birth mother Yu as
Empress Dowager Mingde,]

20:11.910 --> 20:15.530
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

20:13.680 --> 20:16.680
[granting her the right to attend court
behind the screen.]

20:16.680 --> 20:18.830
[He posthumously conferred the title of
Earl of Zhongyong]

20:18.830 --> 20:21.160
[on the late General of Huaihua,
Wei Qilin,]

20:19.630 --> 20:23.840
♪ All people ♪

20:21.920 --> 20:25.050
[and the title of Marquis of Wusu
on the late General Meng Shuyuan.]

20:25.050 --> 20:30.630
♪ Are part of the past ♪

20:26.000 --> 20:29.510
[He specially appointed the Marquis of Wu'an,
Xie Zheng, as Prince Regent,]

20:29.510 --> 20:31.680
[entrusting him with the management
of overall state affairs,]

20:31.680 --> 20:34.690
[and promoted Fan Changyu to
the Grand General of Huaihua,]

20:32.620 --> 20:37.550
♪ What's the date today? ♪

20:35.110 --> 20:37.880
[granting her the title of
First-Rank Lady Protector of the State,]

20:37.880 --> 20:39.200
[together assisting in
the governance of the court.]

20:37.990 --> 20:45.660
♪ How lamentable ♪

20:40.510 --> 20:43.000
[As the new emperor
ascended the throne in his youth,]

20:43.000 --> 20:45.110
[the Three Excellencies stood in balance,]

20:45.110 --> 20:47.160
[both court and country
placed their hopes upon them,]

20:47.160 --> 20:49.690
[and peace prevailed
throughout the realm.]

20:52.440 --> 20:53.790
Long live the Emperor!

20:54.580 --> 20:58.940
♪ All people ♪

20:58.720 --> 21:00.110
Long live the Emperor!

21:00.250 --> 21:05.540
♪ Are part of the past ♪

21:05.640 --> 21:07.400
Long live the Emperor!

21:07.580 --> 21:12.640
♪ What's the date today? ♪

21:12.940 --> 21:20.810
♪ How lamentable ♪

21:13.210 --> 21:19.140
Long live the Emperor!
Long live the Emperor!

21:13.370 --> 21:16.880
[Yin]

21:20.920 --> 21:24.210
[Think with Caution]

21:26.440 --> 21:28.480
Don't forget what you promised me.

21:28.720 --> 21:29.960
Since the Empress Dowager isn't around,

21:29.960 --> 21:31.350
go ahead and eat more.

21:34.270 --> 21:35.670
Don't worry, Changning.

21:35.680 --> 21:37.200
When I take power in the future,

21:37.200 --> 21:39.830
I won't touch the Prince Regent
or the Grand General of Huaihua.

21:39.830 --> 21:42.350
Only incompetent emperors
suspect their subjects.

21:42.350 --> 21:44.110
When you take power in the future,

21:44.110 --> 21:46.440
can you make me a princess?

21:48.960 --> 21:50.360
You want to be a princess?

21:51.200 --> 21:52.550
Yeah, like Miss Royal Physician—

21:52.550 --> 21:53.720
so majestic and impressive.

21:53.720 --> 21:55.160
And when I take a Prince Consort
in the future,

21:55.160 --> 21:58.070
he'll have to bring out his entire
family fortune as the betrothal gift.

21:58.070 --> 22:00.090
All under heaven belongs to me.

22:00.310 --> 22:02.380
No one has a greater fortune than I do.

22:03.270 --> 22:05.070
Do you want to be my Empress?

22:05.110 --> 22:07.960
You're going to give me
the imperial palace as the betrothal gift?

22:07.960 --> 22:10.350
Not just the imperial palace.
The whole realm.

22:10.350 --> 22:11.460
The realm?

22:12.310 --> 22:13.480
What is that?

22:13.750 --> 22:14.920
It's everything—

22:15.550 --> 22:17.640
from the place where Changyu fights wars,

22:17.640 --> 22:18.830
to this imperial palace,

22:18.830 --> 22:20.760
and to all the lands farther south—

22:20.790 --> 22:22.180
all of it belongs to me.

22:22.310 --> 22:23.830
If you become my Empress,

22:23.830 --> 22:25.470
then all of it will be yours.

22:25.880 --> 22:26.880
That big?

22:27.200 --> 22:30.200
Even the falcon would have to fly for days
to get there.

22:31.110 --> 22:32.320
You can't go back on your word.

22:32.320 --> 22:33.770
Let's pinky swear.

22:36.200 --> 22:37.750
Pinky swear.

22:37.750 --> 22:39.200
Cross my heart and hope to die,

22:39.200 --> 22:41.480
stick a needle in my eye.

22:42.240 --> 22:45.260
Qi Yu! How many times did you
have people bring you snacks today?

22:45.260 --> 22:47.310
Aren't you worried you'd get cavities?

22:47.310 --> 22:48.000
Come out!

22:49.960 --> 22:50.760
Get over here!

22:55.510 --> 22:56.030
You really are

22:56.030 --> 22:57.240
getting more and more disobedient,
aren't you?

22:57.240 --> 22:58.720
Fairy Sister, don't hit him.

22:58.720 --> 22:59.850
Changning, be good.

23:00.200 --> 23:01.400
Do you have any idea

23:01.400 --> 23:02.790
how many cavities you already have?

23:02.790 --> 23:04.400
-How dare you run?
-Fairy Sister!

23:04.400 --> 23:05.590
Get over here!

23:17.270 --> 23:18.140
Come here, you!

23:18.000 --> 23:22.650
[Prudent in Action, Mindful of Peril]

23:18.350 --> 23:20.030
You slack off on your studies,

23:20.790 --> 23:22.200
yet you still dare to eat so many sweets?

23:22.200 --> 23:23.100
Get over here!

23:22.660 --> 23:26.060
[Li's Mansion]

23:29.160 --> 23:30.050
Easy. Easy.

23:30.760 --> 23:32.160
Look at this. Seriously.

23:48.160 --> 23:51.460
We're conducting a house confiscation here.
Behave yourself!

23:51.460 --> 23:52.590
Go stand over there.

24:09.270 --> 24:10.070
Grandfather.

24:11.110 --> 24:12.410
Great Yin's wars

24:12.830 --> 24:15.890
against Beijue have left
the state treasury depleted.

24:16.270 --> 24:18.600
Our Li family donating our entire fortune

24:18.830 --> 24:20.960
can be considered an act of atonement.

24:21.030 --> 24:23.750
His Majesty and the Prince Regent
are men of their word.

24:23.750 --> 24:26.080
I believe they'll let bygones be bygones.

24:26.190 --> 24:27.990
Please rest easy, Grandfather,

24:28.440 --> 24:30.170
and live out your days in peace.

24:33.240 --> 24:36.170
What "living out my days in peace"?

24:38.350 --> 24:39.920
It's nothing but

24:40.590 --> 24:42.510
confiscation and exile.

24:45.720 --> 24:49.030
The crimes our Li family committed
are utterly unforgivable.

24:49.030 --> 24:51.430
This is already the best outcome possible.

24:52.200 --> 24:53.960
If they hadn't shown mercy,

24:55.720 --> 24:57.050
I'm afraid the Li family

24:58.110 --> 25:00.240
would have been wiped out completely.

25:06.910 --> 25:09.870
I acted like a villain for nothing.

25:12.180 --> 25:14.790
Seventeen years ago,

25:16.080 --> 25:19.710
I really acted like a villain for nothing.

25:43.510 --> 25:44.680
Wenkan.

25:45.160 --> 25:46.510
Did you really

25:46.510 --> 25:48.590
request to be exiled to the frontier,

25:49.000 --> 25:51.880
to suffer in that bitter, desolate place?

26:01.730 --> 26:02.680
Perhaps

26:04.480 --> 26:07.080
this is the best arrangement
fate has to offer.

26:27.930 --> 26:36.930
[Lin'an]

26:33.440 --> 26:35.670
Changyu, you're back!

26:35.690 --> 26:37.680
Changyu, you're back!

26:38.440 --> 26:40.260
Changyu!

26:40.280 --> 26:42.460
Changyu, I missed you so much!

26:43.830 --> 26:45.780
Changyu, you're back!

26:45.920 --> 26:47.880
-Changyu!
-You're back!

26:48.400 --> 26:50.160
Changyu, you're back!

26:50.500 --> 26:52.330
Changyu, you're back!

26:52.550 --> 26:53.920
Changyu, you're back!

26:55.310 --> 26:56.790
Mrs. Fan!

26:56.880 --> 26:58.000
Changyu!

26:58.750 --> 26:59.620
Changyu!

26:59.680 --> 27:01.290
Mrs. Fan!

27:01.480 --> 27:05.160
-Greetings, Grand General of Huaihua!
-Greetings, Grand General of Huaihua!

27:05.160 --> 27:05.590
Please.

27:05.590 --> 27:07.730
Grand General of Huaihua!

27:08.070 --> 27:10.280
-Dear!
-Changyu, you're back!

27:10.510 --> 27:11.720
Mrs. Fan!

27:12.670 --> 27:14.820
[Luo's Pawnshop]

27:13.310 --> 27:14.960
Mrs. Fan, you're back.

27:15.330 --> 27:17.170
Mrs. Fan, you're back!

27:20.550 --> 27:21.310
Changyu!

27:22.630 --> 27:23.760
You're back.

27:26.070 --> 27:28.200
-Grand General of Huaihua!
-Mrs. Fan!

27:29.960 --> 27:31.430
Changyu.

27:31.550 --> 27:32.880
Changyu!

27:32.900 --> 27:33.900
Changyu!

27:34.110 --> 27:35.130
Changyu!

27:37.840 --> 27:38.780
You're back!

27:43.030 --> 27:44.430
Changyu, you're back.

27:56.920 --> 28:01.290
♪ In the east wind,
flowers bloom at night ♪

28:02.220 --> 28:05.350
♪ Blowing down the stars like rain ♪

28:07.650 --> 28:09.850
♪ Fine horses and carved carriages
fill the fragrant streets ♪

28:10.300 --> 28:12.300
♪ The phoenix flute resounds ♪

28:12.820 --> 28:14.110
♪ The jade pot light revolves ♪

28:14.370 --> 28:18.150
♪ A night of fish-and-dragon dances ♪

28:14.960 --> 28:16.750
You must've waited for this moment

28:16.750 --> 28:17.840
for a long time.

28:18.290 --> 28:22.890
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

28:22.910 --> 28:27.910
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

28:28.470 --> 28:30.650
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

28:31.210 --> 28:35.700
♪ I find her there ♪

28:36.040 --> 28:45.530
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

28:37.230 --> 28:41.280
[Memorial Tablet of Wei Qilin]
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]

28:39.000 --> 28:43.240
Please bless Changyu and the other kids
to return soon.

28:46.070 --> 28:48.440
Dear, that's enough.

28:48.830 --> 28:50.920
Good people like Changyu and the others
are watched over by Heaven.

28:50.920 --> 28:52.480
They'll surely be alright.

28:52.480 --> 28:54.160
How could you men possibly

28:55.000 --> 28:56.310
understand what it feels like for a mother

28:56.310 --> 28:59.110
to have her own flesh and blood
taken away from her?

28:59.350 --> 29:00.960
Have we no shame?

29:01.880 --> 29:04.960
You think we could just claim to be
the Grand General of Huaihua's parents?

29:04.960 --> 29:06.680
What are you thinking?

29:09.000 --> 29:10.130
Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:12.850 --> 29:13.820
Dear.

29:14.000 --> 29:15.350
Dear, listen.

29:15.890 --> 29:17.450
We're back!

29:17.960 --> 29:19.000
Is that Changning's voice?

29:19.000 --> 29:22.200
-You miss them so much you're imagining things.
-Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:22.200 --> 29:22.720
Listen.

29:22.720 --> 29:24.100
Listen to what?

29:24.400 --> 29:25.530
Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:28.960 --> 29:29.680
It's real!

29:29.970 --> 29:31.390
They really are back.

29:32.200 --> 29:32.930
Is anyone...

29:34.770 --> 29:35.930
Mr. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

29:37.790 --> 29:38.680
Changyu.

29:39.720 --> 29:40.680
Changyu!

29:42.000 --> 29:43.260
Changyu, you're back!

29:43.260 --> 29:44.190
Mr. Zhao.

29:44.920 --> 29:45.590
Mrs. Zhao.

29:45.880 --> 29:46.740
You're tanned,

29:46.780 --> 29:48.270
and you've lost weight, kid.

29:48.270 --> 29:49.680
You must have been through a lot.

29:49.680 --> 29:51.810
You're home now. That's what matters.

29:53.200 --> 29:53.960
Godmother.

29:54.920 --> 29:55.640
Godfather.

29:56.270 --> 29:57.830
I came back in one piece.

29:58.880 --> 30:00.880
I'll take care of you two from now on,

30:01.110 --> 30:02.240
and we'll never be apart again.

30:02.240 --> 30:03.970
I'll take care of you, too.

30:05.240 --> 30:06.040
Changyu.

30:06.880 --> 30:08.220
What did you call us?

30:08.350 --> 30:09.750
On the way back, Changyu

30:09.830 --> 30:11.070
kept thinking about

30:11.240 --> 30:12.550
changing how she addresses you.

30:12.550 --> 30:14.400
Please grant her wish.

30:15.750 --> 30:16.350
Sure.

30:16.680 --> 30:20.050
We don't deserve such a blessing.

30:20.550 --> 30:23.280
You're not leaving, right?
That's the best news.

30:23.440 --> 30:25.440
No matter how high-ranking
the officials you've met,

30:25.440 --> 30:26.790
or how much of the world you've seen,

30:26.790 --> 30:27.880
nothing compares to home.

30:27.880 --> 30:30.680
Nothing compares to
having parents around, kids.

30:31.510 --> 30:33.400
We won't be separated again, kids.

30:33.400 --> 30:35.400
We'll never be apart again.

30:36.160 --> 30:37.660
Mr. Zhao. Mrs. Zhao.

30:37.830 --> 30:38.790
We're back!

30:41.110 --> 30:44.170
Mr. Zhao. Mrs. Zhao.
We're back safe and sound.

30:44.270 --> 30:46.930
From now on,
we'll take care of you two together.

30:52.510 --> 30:53.710
Jin Yuanbao.

30:54.070 --> 30:55.310
You've matured.

30:56.070 --> 30:57.440
Come on, get up.

30:59.000 --> 30:59.920
Mancang.

31:00.270 --> 31:02.070
You're still so strong.

31:04.240 --> 31:04.960
Manwu.

31:04.960 --> 31:05.820
Mrs. Zhao.

31:07.790 --> 31:09.200
W-Where is Mandi?

31:09.680 --> 31:11.720
There's one missing.

31:14.070 --> 31:14.790
Godmother.

31:17.590 --> 31:18.880
Mandi...

31:19.640 --> 31:20.900
He didn't make it back.

31:29.880 --> 31:32.270
Why does there have to be one missing?

31:34.240 --> 31:35.310
Good kid.

31:35.720 --> 31:36.910
You're home now.

31:37.030 --> 31:38.160
That's what matters.

31:38.160 --> 31:39.390
You're home now.

31:39.960 --> 31:41.750
Quick, come inside.

31:41.750 --> 31:43.960
-Come on in.
-Come on in.

31:43.960 --> 31:44.510
Come.

31:44.720 --> 31:46.240
We're home, Changning.

31:46.440 --> 31:47.180
We're home.

31:54.850 --> 32:04.740
[Memorial Tablet of Late Friend Zisu]
[Memorial Tablet of Late Friend Fuling]

32:15.720 --> 32:24.810
[May Mercy Guide All to Salvation]

32:19.750 --> 32:20.440
Mother.

32:21.510 --> 32:22.000
Mother!

32:22.000 --> 32:22.800
Your Majesty.

32:22.830 --> 32:26.100
You should address the Empress Dowager
as Imperial Mother.

32:26.100 --> 32:27.700
Imperial Mother, come here.

32:33.420 --> 32:34.180
What is it?

32:35.510 --> 32:37.680
Imperial Mother, I want to issue a decree

32:37.680 --> 32:39.920
and make Changning my Empress.

32:41.240 --> 32:41.830
Then you have to ask

32:41.830 --> 32:43.890
whether Changning is willing or not.

32:44.400 --> 32:47.200
Last time, Changning asked me
to make her a princess.

32:47.200 --> 32:48.310
I refused

32:48.340 --> 32:50.480
and told her I'd make her Empress instead.

32:50.480 --> 32:52.160
Changning has already agreed.

32:52.160 --> 32:53.730
We even pinky-swore on it.

32:55.590 --> 32:56.790
That still won't do.

32:57.440 --> 32:58.480
Why?

32:59.200 --> 33:01.200
Because you are both still too young.

33:01.200 --> 33:03.350
You can only get married when you grow up.

33:03.350 --> 33:04.880
Wait until your coming-of-age ceremony—

33:04.880 --> 33:06.110
then you can go ask Changning.

33:06.110 --> 33:06.720
Alright.

33:09.030 --> 33:10.110
It's snowing.

33:32.110 --> 33:33.440
It's a quarter to 12 now—

33:36.170 --> 33:37.830
time for Wei Yan's execution.

33:53.480 --> 33:54.450
Yigui.

33:55.160 --> 33:58.380
Jiuheng prepared this wine for you
personally,

33:59.240 --> 34:00.700
to save you from suffering

34:03.290 --> 34:05.210
the pain of a lingering death.

34:31.840 --> 34:33.730
It's the time of heavy snow again.

34:35.590 --> 34:39.920
It's the time of heavy snow again.

34:44.550 --> 34:46.719
Did you make your uncle angry again?

34:46.920 --> 34:48.889
Uncle's teaching is so hard,

34:49.070 --> 34:50.230
and he has no patience.

34:50.230 --> 34:51.429
He keeps scolding me.

34:52.840 --> 34:53.750
Uncle.

34:53.920 --> 34:54.940
I won.

35:04.280 --> 35:05.630
You're finally here.

35:39.230 --> 35:40.290
It's getting late.

35:42.840 --> 35:44.370
It's time for you to go back.

36:10.890 --> 36:13.110
[Wei Yan, who once served as Chancellor,
though achieved great merit in assisting governance,]

36:13.130 --> 36:15.190
[could not atone for his crimes. First, there was
the tragic death of 100,000 soldiers in Jinzhou;]

36:15.220 --> 36:18.260
[and later, the relentless flames of war at the frontier.
He brought disaster upon the state, abandoned the loyal,]

36:18.280 --> 36:21.920
[deceived the people, and slew his own kin.
One who destroys the moral order]

36:19.400 --> 36:21.670
Be a good pig in this life,

36:21.940 --> 36:22.400
[and uses the common people as kindling,
even while raising the banner of universal peace,]

36:22.510 --> 36:23.710
and a good person

36:22.940 --> 36:24.400
[commits a crime of the highest magnitude
and must be executed.]

36:24.420 --> 36:26.120
[His family property was confiscated;
his lifetime of merits and faults is left for posterity to judge.]

36:24.760 --> 36:26.920
in the next.

36:28.110 --> 36:30.030
People like me

36:32.470 --> 36:35.150
will probably fall straight into hell.

36:37.760 --> 36:40.160
I'm afraid there won't be a next life
for me.

37:00.160 --> 37:05.420
[Two months later]

37:09.920 --> 37:10.800
You know what?

37:11.190 --> 37:13.000
Ever since we returned to Xigu Lane,

37:13.000 --> 37:15.920
this tree has somehow become
"the matchmaking tree."

37:15.920 --> 37:18.820
They say the romance between
the Grand General of Huaihua

37:18.820 --> 37:20.440
and the Prince Regent
began right here under this tree.

37:20.440 --> 37:22.400
How did the rumors turn out like this?

37:22.400 --> 37:24.840
Didn't you pick me up
from the snowy river crossing?

37:23.190 --> 37:25.290
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

37:25.030 --> 37:27.400
Anyway, they say this tree works wonders.

37:26.460 --> 37:27.600
♪ With very pale colors ♪

37:27.590 --> 37:29.960
As long as you toss your red ribbon
up into the tree,

37:28.730 --> 37:31.380
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

37:30.030 --> 37:31.630
the one whose ribbon becomes
entwined with yours

37:31.630 --> 37:33.950
is your destined one.

37:31.870 --> 37:34.160
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

37:34.110 --> 37:35.510
You're quite superstitious.

37:35.120 --> 37:36.450
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

37:35.510 --> 37:36.280
It's true.

37:36.480 --> 37:37.840
Many people met their destined ones

37:37.280 --> 37:41.520
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

37:38.030 --> 37:39.920
after making wishes here.

37:45.100 --> 37:47.440
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

37:48.390 --> 37:49.850
♪ The light shines ♪

37:50.690 --> 37:53.280
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

37:52.280 --> 37:54.860
Do we have to sneak around like thieves

37:53.860 --> 37:56.240
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

37:54.920 --> 37:56.580
in the middle of the night?

37:57.040 --> 37:58.750
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

37:58.230 --> 38:01.140
If people saw us, the protagonists
of the story, coming here to pray ourselves,

37:59.240 --> 38:04.070
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

38:01.510 --> 38:03.710
they'd probably laugh their heads off.

38:06.600 --> 38:07.840
♪ I pray that our love ♪

38:07.860 --> 38:10.400
♪ Will never end ♪

38:11.010 --> 38:12.040
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

38:12.070 --> 38:12.970
You go first.

38:12.090 --> 38:14.300
♪ For a lifetime ♪

38:14.630 --> 38:15.280
Scared?

38:15.060 --> 38:18.990
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

38:16.110 --> 38:17.570
I'm the head of the family,

38:17.710 --> 38:19.450
so it's only right
that mine entwines with yours.

38:19.450 --> 38:23.090
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

38:20.840 --> 38:21.360
Okay.

38:23.940 --> 38:24.830
♪ I pray that our love ♪

38:24.850 --> 38:27.450
♪ Will not be like sand
slipping into the sea ♪

38:26.280 --> 38:26.920
Go ahead.

38:28.750 --> 38:29.670
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

38:29.690 --> 38:32.060
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

38:30.560 --> 38:31.370
Please, entwine with his.

38:31.370 --> 38:32.370
Entwine with his.

38:32.600 --> 38:36.660
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

38:37.090 --> 38:45.380
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

38:39.190 --> 38:40.030
This doesn't count.

38:40.030 --> 38:40.590
What are you doing?

38:40.590 --> 38:41.650
I'm doing it again.

38:42.400 --> 38:44.280
I have to take it down and throw it again.

38:44.280 --> 38:45.590
Mine didn't entwine with yours.

38:45.590 --> 38:46.400
It's okay.

38:46.510 --> 38:47.480
It already did.

38:47.670 --> 38:48.590
How so? Look, I don't even know

38:48.590 --> 38:51.390
-whose ribbon mine is entwined with...
-Trust me.

38:51.760 --> 38:52.600
In this life,

38:53.230 --> 38:54.030
the next life,

38:54.480 --> 38:55.540
for all lifetimes,

38:56.510 --> 38:58.570
the two of us will always be entwined.

38:59.070 --> 39:01.600
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

39:02.360 --> 39:03.880
♪ The light shines ♪

39:02.630 --> 39:03.800
But I still have to take it down.

39:03.800 --> 39:04.760
Let's go.

39:04.660 --> 39:07.380
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

39:05.550 --> 39:06.940
Put me down.

39:07.030 --> 39:07.600
No.

39:07.710 --> 39:08.530
Do you hear me?

39:07.830 --> 39:10.410
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

39:08.670 --> 39:09.600
I can't hear you.

39:10.190 --> 39:11.320
I have to go back.

39:11.010 --> 39:12.820
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

39:13.220 --> 39:18.200
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

39:18.100 --> 39:21.360
[Changyu and Zheng, for all lifetimes]

39:20.570 --> 39:21.810
♪ I pray that our love ♪

39:21.830 --> 39:24.440
♪ Will never end ♪

39:25.000 --> 39:26.160
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

39:26.190 --> 39:28.460
♪ For a lifetime ♪

39:29.030 --> 39:32.960
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

39:33.420 --> 39:37.230
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

39:37.910 --> 39:38.950
♪ I pray that our love ♪

39:38.970 --> 39:41.520
♪ Will not be like sand
slipping into the sea ♪

39:42.720 --> 39:43.640
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

39:43.670 --> 39:46.030
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

39:46.580 --> 39:50.630
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

39:51.060 --> 40:02.830
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

40:06.590 --> 40:12.450
♪ Clear and quiet ♪

40:14.250 --> 40:20.140
[Five years later]
[Jinzhou Barracks]

40:20.630 --> 40:22.760
It's been years
since we last came to the barracks.

40:22.760 --> 40:24.360
Memories are flashing back.

40:25.150 --> 40:25.710
Yeah.

40:26.510 --> 40:27.320
Assemble!

40:30.760 --> 40:31.360
Assemble!

40:31.480 --> 40:31.940
Assemble!

40:31.940 --> 40:32.540
Hurry up!

40:32.710 --> 40:34.400
Greetings, Prince Regent and
Grand General of Huaihua.

40:34.400 --> 40:35.360
Beijue is invading.

40:35.360 --> 40:37.510
The Blood-Robed Cavalry is assembling.

40:37.510 --> 40:39.920
Dear, I'll have someone send you back
to Lin'an.

40:39.920 --> 40:41.030
What are you talking about?

40:41.030 --> 40:41.710
I'm going with you.

40:41.710 --> 40:42.440
Nonsense.

40:43.000 --> 40:44.280
You haven't been to the battlefield
in years.

40:44.280 --> 40:45.670
Don't underestimate me.

40:45.670 --> 40:46.880
My title of General of Huaihua

40:46.880 --> 40:48.670
wasn't earned without plenty of battles.

40:48.670 --> 40:49.320
Someone!

40:50.070 --> 40:50.550
Yes.

40:50.550 --> 40:51.510
Bring my armor.

40:51.510 --> 40:52.070
Yes.

41:10.510 --> 41:11.030
Whoa!

41:12.510 --> 41:13.550
General Xie.

41:13.760 --> 41:15.280
If you encounter any danger,

41:15.280 --> 41:16.140
hide behind me.

41:16.880 --> 41:18.480
You're already mother of two.

41:18.480 --> 41:19.740
Grow up a bit, alright?

41:20.480 --> 41:22.480
Then let's be careful in all things.

41:22.670 --> 41:23.870
May we return safely.

41:24.000 --> 41:25.200
May we return safely.

41:26.840 --> 41:27.280
Hyah!

41:27.510 --> 41:28.070
Hyah!

41:29.480 --> 41:30.070
Hyah!

41:40.260 --> 41:44.060
[The End]

41:44.720 --> 41:47.120
[Post-Credits Scene]

41:49.300 --> 41:53.750
[If the Jinzhou Massacre 17 years ago
had never happened]

42:00.630 --> 42:03.430
Zheng is really diligent with
his sword practice.

42:05.070 --> 42:06.590
A few days ago,

42:06.750 --> 42:08.270
his father pointed out

42:08.290 --> 42:10.290
that his sword moves weren't solid.

42:10.400 --> 42:11.530
These past few days,

42:11.550 --> 42:13.550
apart from eating, sleeping, and studying,

42:13.550 --> 42:14.670
he's spent all his time here

42:14.670 --> 42:16.280
practicing swordsmanship.

42:18.480 --> 42:19.810
He's been this stubborn

42:19.840 --> 42:22.060
since childhood.

42:22.280 --> 42:24.360
He's not like me at all,

42:24.650 --> 42:25.860
nor his father.

42:26.710 --> 42:28.110
He's more like his uncle.

42:30.030 --> 42:31.590
"A nephew takes after his uncle."

42:31.590 --> 42:33.510
That saying exists for a reason.

42:36.630 --> 42:38.400
This one in my belly

42:38.400 --> 42:39.920
is quite lazy, though—

42:40.400 --> 42:41.550
full-term already,

42:41.890 --> 42:43.540
yet barely any movement.

42:44.070 --> 42:45.150
I'm guessing

42:46.110 --> 42:49.020
it's a quiet girl.

42:50.890 --> 42:52.480
But when her father teased her,

42:52.480 --> 42:54.440
she made such a commotion

42:54.440 --> 42:56.970
that he couldn't sleep all night,

42:57.070 --> 42:59.130
and with a worried frown, he asked me,

42:59.480 --> 43:01.230
"what if it's a boy?"

43:02.920 --> 43:03.920
How come?

43:03.920 --> 43:06.730
General Wei likes daughters so much?

43:07.590 --> 43:09.840
He was grinning from ear to ear
when he said to me,

43:09.840 --> 43:11.560
"if it's a girl,

43:11.710 --> 43:13.030
we'll name her Changyu."

43:13.030 --> 43:14.400
And what if it's a boy?

43:14.510 --> 43:16.110
He said boys are tough,

43:16.480 --> 43:18.710
so we'll call him "Iron Ball"

43:18.880 --> 43:20.180
or "Bull" for now.

43:20.710 --> 43:21.630
When he grows up,

43:21.630 --> 43:24.430
we'll have his grandfather give him
a proper name.

43:28.510 --> 43:29.880
I heard

43:30.070 --> 43:31.960
there's a folk method

43:32.880 --> 43:36.070
where a young child can tell

43:36.480 --> 43:38.400
if a pregnant woman is carrying
a boy or a girl.

43:38.400 --> 43:39.360
Want to try?

43:39.360 --> 43:40.010
Sure.

43:40.360 --> 43:41.190
Zheng.

43:42.280 --> 43:44.070
Come here to Mother.

43:46.590 --> 43:47.960
Let me ask you—

43:48.630 --> 43:50.660
what do you think, is Mrs. Meng

43:50.880 --> 43:53.550
carrying a boy or a girl?

43:57.480 --> 43:58.280
A girl.

44:00.550 --> 44:02.070
If it's a girl,

44:02.230 --> 44:03.510
how about you marry her

44:03.920 --> 44:05.780
and make her my daughter-in-law?

44:06.550 --> 44:08.840
Why should she be your daughter-in-law?

44:11.800 --> 44:14.110
Because I like her.

44:19.740 --> 44:20.380
Okay.

44:41.960 --> 44:43.820
If it's a girl,

44:43.880 --> 44:45.250
we'll name her Changyu.

44:47.640 --> 44:52.890
[Chang]

44:57.030 --> 45:00.080
[Changyu]

45:00.170 --> 45:05.520
[Verdure Soaring to the Clouds]

45:04.630 --> 45:05.800
Greetings, My Lady.

45:06.360 --> 45:07.280
Thank you for coming, Nanny.

45:07.280 --> 45:08.610
So? Has she given birth?

45:08.760 --> 45:11.070
Yes. Both mother and daughter are
safe and healthy.

45:11.070 --> 45:13.190
She specially sent me to
bring the good news.

45:13.190 --> 45:14.150
Thank you for your trouble, Nanny.

45:14.150 --> 45:15.750
Come on, please come inside.

45:17.630 --> 45:19.490
It was really considerate of her.

45:19.630 --> 45:20.960
I've also prepared a small gift

45:20.960 --> 45:22.820
as a token of my congratulations.

45:23.510 --> 45:24.280
Thank you.

45:24.880 --> 45:26.360
How's her health?

45:27.440 --> 45:28.760
She's doing well.

45:29.190 --> 45:30.920
Please pass a message to her for me,
Nanny.

45:30.920 --> 45:32.710
Tell her I'll come visit in a few days.

45:32.710 --> 45:33.550
Alright.

45:34.000 --> 45:35.550
Please, no need to see me out, My Lady.

45:35.550 --> 45:36.710
Thank you, Nanny.

45:37.270 --> 45:42.050
[Verdure Soaring to the Clouds]

45:51.510 --> 45:53.880
Mother, did Mrs. Meng give birth?

45:54.190 --> 45:55.150
Yes.

45:56.190 --> 45:57.000
What,

45:57.800 --> 46:01.330
are you already thinking about
your little future wife, Zheng?

46:08.880 --> 46:13.300
[Changyu's Birthday]

46:16.980 --> 46:24.700
[Changyu's Birthday:
January 17, 5th Year of Qinghe]

46:27.200 --> 46:33.270
[16 years later]

46:29.510 --> 46:30.710
Over the past 5 years,

46:30.840 --> 46:32.510
Father has finally worn down
the Beijue army

46:32.510 --> 46:34.910
until their treasury is nearly exhausted.

46:35.030 --> 46:36.760
For those old relics in the court

46:36.760 --> 46:38.280
to propose a ceasefire now—

46:38.280 --> 46:40.230
wouldn't that be plainly giving
the Beijue forces

46:40.230 --> 46:41.150
a chance to rest, recover,

46:41.150 --> 46:42.550
and make a comeback?

46:44.390 --> 46:46.510
I've come to the Capital this time
on my father's behalf

46:46.510 --> 46:48.480
to persuade His Majesty

46:48.670 --> 46:49.760
to continue sending troops,

46:49.760 --> 46:51.190
strike straight at
the Beijue army's stronghold,

46:51.190 --> 46:53.520
and eliminate the threat once and for all.

46:53.590 --> 46:55.030
But do you really think

46:55.400 --> 46:58.460
it was those old ministers
who proposed the ceasefire?

47:01.030 --> 47:02.880
The wars your father has fought
these past years

47:02.880 --> 47:04.610
have been steady and measured.

47:05.400 --> 47:06.360
His aim has been

47:06.760 --> 47:08.630
to wear down the Beijue army

47:09.000 --> 47:11.060
and drag them into total exhaustion.

47:12.150 --> 47:15.230
But His Majesty doesn't see it that way.

47:16.480 --> 47:18.030
But my father has always been

47:18.030 --> 47:19.690
utterly loyal to His Majesty.

47:20.670 --> 47:22.070
Twenty years ago,

47:22.070 --> 47:25.960
His Majesty was just as virtuous and loyal

47:26.150 --> 47:28.150
as the current Crown Prince, Qi Min.

47:28.850 --> 47:30.670
Yet over the years,

47:30.670 --> 47:32.920
his attitude toward the Eastern Palace

47:33.320 --> 47:36.980
has always been one of caution,
fearing a repeat of past troubles.

47:37.550 --> 47:39.190
He even guards against

47:39.630 --> 47:41.320
his own son so heavily,

47:41.960 --> 47:44.670
let alone those marquises of different clans
stationed in the Northwest,

47:44.670 --> 47:48.190
holding 100,000 troops.

47:48.190 --> 47:51.000
How could he simply let them
act as they please?

47:54.440 --> 47:55.150
Alright.

47:55.880 --> 47:58.670
Put aside the counterattack on Beijue
for now.

47:59.590 --> 48:00.990
When you see His Majesty,

48:01.110 --> 48:02.360
if you bring it up again,

48:02.360 --> 48:03.880
His Majesty will still use

48:04.320 --> 48:07.880
things like the floods in the south

48:07.880 --> 48:09.150
as an excuse.

48:13.510 --> 48:15.330
Thank you for your advice, Uncle.

48:15.330 --> 48:16.080
Come on.

48:16.590 --> 48:17.190
By the way,

48:17.670 --> 48:19.800
your aunt has made some food.

48:19.960 --> 48:20.960
Let's have a bite.

48:22.670 --> 48:23.670
Now,

48:23.670 --> 48:26.710
you can finally have a few drinks with me.

48:27.440 --> 48:30.850
Now, neither Father nor General Wei
can out-drink me.

48:31.070 --> 48:33.930
Then I'll measure myself
against you today, Uncle.

48:34.800 --> 48:36.670
You've really grown up, huh?

48:37.060 --> 48:44.770
[Received Grace, Cherished Favor]

48:37.630 --> 48:38.430
Alright then.

48:38.670 --> 48:42.000
Let's settle this at the table.

48:42.000 --> 48:42.600
After you.

48:46.380 --> 48:48.840
[Yixiang Restaurant]

48:46.960 --> 48:48.760
Ladies. This way, please.

48:48.760 --> 48:49.480
Alright.

48:53.550 --> 48:54.150
Please.

49:03.800 --> 49:05.630
-Watch your step.
-For some unknown reason,

49:05.630 --> 49:06.440
since coming to Lin'an,

49:06.440 --> 49:08.700
I've felt a sudden sense of familiarity.

49:14.230 --> 49:16.960
You two must be noble guests
from the Capital too.

49:17.070 --> 49:17.920
Upstairs, please.

49:17.920 --> 49:20.450
The other guests are already
waiting for you.

49:21.360 --> 49:22.230
Manager.

49:23.270 --> 49:24.870
You look a bit familiar.

49:25.480 --> 49:27.360
Have we met somewhere before?

49:29.000 --> 49:30.230
I don't know why,

49:30.590 --> 49:32.120
but now that you mention it,

49:32.320 --> 49:33.480
I feel the same way.

49:34.590 --> 49:35.550
Maybe in a past life,

49:35.550 --> 49:37.150
we were truly close friends.

49:37.960 --> 49:38.630
Dear,

49:38.630 --> 49:40.630
let me treat you to our specialties.

49:41.760 --> 49:42.290
Let's go.

49:44.840 --> 49:46.440
You've all had a long journey.

49:46.440 --> 49:47.570
Let's drink to that.

49:47.880 --> 49:49.000
-Come on.
-Cheers.

49:49.400 --> 49:50.420
Thank you all for your hard work.

49:50.420 --> 49:51.100
Bottoms up.

50:00.450 --> 50:01.910
Sorry to keep you waiting.

50:10.710 --> 50:13.110
This is our Yixiang Restaurant's
signature Hasma Soup.

50:13.110 --> 50:14.840
Please enjoy, honored guests.

50:15.440 --> 50:17.500
-It smells pretty good.
-Hasma Soup?

50:18.330 --> 50:19.130
Smells great.

50:32.820 --> 50:35.070
Honored guest, would you like a taste?

50:49.630 --> 50:51.830
Are you feeling unwell, honored guest?

50:59.040 --> 51:00.250
I'll go get changed.

51:00.960 --> 51:02.420
Please enjoy yourselves.

51:16.190 --> 51:17.110
Honored guest.

51:17.480 --> 51:19.080
Are you sure you're alright?

51:20.670 --> 51:21.400
I'm fine.

51:21.630 --> 51:23.890
Manager, you may go about your business.

51:26.800 --> 51:28.800
The soup is so good, yet you threw up.

51:29.030 --> 51:31.090
I'm so pretty, yet you threw up again.

51:31.590 --> 51:32.920
Utterly baffling.

51:38.760 --> 51:40.560
Are you alright, Your Highness?

51:44.110 --> 51:46.360
Your Highness is usually most courteous.

51:46.360 --> 51:47.440
Why are you

51:47.760 --> 51:50.160
so repulsed by a restaurant manager today?

51:50.230 --> 51:52.030
The food taster tried that soup just now,

51:52.030 --> 51:54.030
and there was nothing wrong with it.

51:55.510 --> 51:57.240
I don't know the reason either.

51:58.670 --> 52:00.800
Perhaps we were enemies in a past life.

52:02.230 --> 52:03.190
When I saw her,

52:03.840 --> 52:05.440
my heart was filled with joy,

52:05.840 --> 52:07.260
yet I couldn't get close.

52:08.190 --> 52:10.320
The moment I did, I felt like vomiting.

52:12.480 --> 52:15.010
Perhaps this is what people mean
when they say

52:15.840 --> 52:16.960
some connections are fated
but not meant to be.
